               <msContents>
                  <summary>Gospel of John, ወንጌል፡ ዘዮሐንስ፡, Canticles of Flower, ማሕሌተ፡ ጽጌ፡, Lamentations of the Virgin, ሰቆቃወ፡ ድንግል፡, Image of Mary of Qwəsqwam, Reward for reading the Gospel regularly</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from = "1r" to = "94r"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT1693John"/>
                  <note>
                    Arranged for the days of the week (
                    Saturday, <locus target = "#18v"/>;
                    Tuesday, <locus target = "#23v"/>;
                    Saturday, <locus target = "#42r"/>;
                    Wednesday, <locus target = "#50v"/>;
                    Thursday, <locus target = "#61r"/>;
                    Friday, <locus target = "#77v"/>;
                    Sunday, <locus target = "#87r"/>;
                    Everyday, <locus target = "#92r"/>).
                    Text, <locus target = "#1r"/>; Conclusion, <foreign xml:lang = "gez">መልአ</foreign>, <locus target = "#93v"/>
                  </note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from = "94r" to = "122r"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT1834Mahlet"/>
                  <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                    ጽጌ፡ አስተርአየ፡ ሠሪዖ፡ እምዓፅሙ። ለዘአምኃኪ፡ ጽጌ፡ ለገብርኤል፡ ምስለ፡ ሰላም።...
                  </incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from = "122r" to = "132r"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT2285Saqoqa"/></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4"><locus from = "132v" to = "135r"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT1862Malkea"/></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5"><locus from = "135v" to = "136v"/><title>Reward for reading the Gospel regularly</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                    ኦአኃው፡ ስምዑ፡ ዘወሀበ፡ ተስፋ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ለውሉደ፡ አዳም፡ ወዘያነብብ፡ ወንጌለ፡ እንበለ፡ አጽርዖ፡...
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>

