                  <additions>
                    <list>
                      <item xml:id = "a1">
                        <desc><locus target = "#iv #iir"/> Prayer for salvation from the sea of fire, hell, <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ድርሳነ፡ ቀሌምንጦስ፡</foreign>. Our Lord’s sufferings during Passion Week are invoked in the prayer
                        with incipit
                        <foreign xml:lang = "gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡...ድርሳን፡ ዘብፁዕ፡ ቀሌምንጦስ፡ ስምዕ፡ ኵሎ፡ ጊዜ፡ ከመ፡ ያውፅዕ፡ ነፍስተ፡ ፩እመሂ፡ ነፍስተ፡ ብዙኃ፡ ጸሎተ፡ እግዚኦ፡ ዘኃደግነ፡ ለነ፡ ትእምርተ፡ ሕማማቲከ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሰንዱን፡ በዘቦቱ፡ ተገንዘ፡ ሥጋከ፡ ቅዱስ፡...</foreign>
                      </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id = "a2">
                        <desc type = "Asmat">
                          Asmat prayer to brighten the mind, with incipit
                          <foreign xml:lang = "gez">
                            ሰድርቃኤል፡ አብድርቃኤል፡ አፍናፌድ፡ ዮሴዴ፡ አትሪኮን፡ ቦርፎሪኮን፡ አትርጌዎን፡ ስጥጥ፡ ግልባቤ፡ ልብየ፡...
                          </foreign>
                        </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id = "a3">
                        <desc type = "Asmat">
                          <locus target = "#136v"/> Asmat prayer whose purpose is not stated, with incipit
                          <foreign xml:lang = "gez">
                            አልቅያኖስ፡ ዘሎሚ፡ ትረትዕ፡ አቁም፡ በጠጁን፡ ዘሐጁን፡ ከረዙን፡...
                          </foreign>
                        </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id = "a4">
                        <desc><locus target = "#137r #137v"/> Calendar of the Apostles and Evangelists</desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id ="a5">
                        <desc type = "Asmat"><locus target = "#138r"/> Fragment of prayer against pestilence with the asmat preserved in the <title ref = "LIT1295Dersan"/></desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id = "a6">
                        <desc>Verso of the rearguard leaf: an attempt to write the different forms of <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ሀ</foreign></desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id = "a7">
                        <desc type = "OwnershipNote">Note of ownership by <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ገብረ፡ ሚካኤል፡</foreign>, <locus target = "#1r #135r"/> and passim,
                        and <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ወልደ፡ ሐና፡</foreign>, <locus target = "#94r"/> and passim</desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id = "a8">
                        <desc>Copied by <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ፄወ፡ ኢየሱስ፡</foreign>, <locus target = "#1r #94r"/> and passim</desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id = "a9">
                        <desc>
                          Overlooked words of text are written interlinearly (<locus target = "#14v #18v #34v #39v #40r #47v #53r"/>, etc.);
                          and overlooked lines of text are written interlinearly (<locus target = "#32v #44v #75v"/>, );
                          and in the upper margin with a symbol (+) marking the location where the text is to be inserted (<locus target = "#131v"/>, line 14),
                          and in another case where text was overlooked due to homoeoteleuton where the symbol (|-o) is used (<locus target = "#15r"/>, line 11)
                        </desc>
                      </item>

                      <item xml:id = "e1">
                        <desc><locus target = "#ir"/> blank</desc>
